  "text": "In this section, we briefly present an introduction to DiffCat, proposed by Kawrykow and Robillard, which detects and removes non-essential changes [CITATION_1] . Next, we highlight the difference between essential changes, which are the treatments of a bug, and the root causes of the bug.",
